# i386 architecture configuration for libengine (freestanding LplPlugin).
#
# Determinism (HARD contract): all float math goes through SSE (-msse2
# -mfpmath=sse) with contraction disabled (-ffp-contract=off) so results are
# IEEE-exact and bit-identical to the Linux/xmake oracle, which is built with
# the matching -ffp-contract=off. Authoritative state is Fixed32 (integer);
# these flags only fix the non-authoritative float paths and the compile-time
# CORDIC table folding.
# -fno-math-errno: __builtin_sqrt etc. fold to a bare sqrtsd instead of a libm
# call with errno bookkeeping. Freestanding has no libm/errno, and the errno
# side effect is itself non-deterministic — dropping it is both necessary to
# link and correct for the determinism contract (the returned value is the same
# IEEE-exact sqrtsd result either way).
# -mstackrealign: with -mfpmath=sse the compiler emits ALIGNED SSE moves
# (movaps/movdqa) to stack temporaries, which #GP-fault unless the stack is
# 16-byte aligned. The i386 kernel does not yet guarantee a 16-byte aligned
# stack on entry (proper FPU/SSE stack setup is a later phase), and an IRQ can
# perturb alignment, so every engine function realigns its own frame. This is
# a pure prologue adjustment — it does not change any computed (IEEE) result.
ARCH_CXXFLAGS=-msse2 -mfpmath=sse -ffp-contract=off -fno-math-errno -mstackrealign
ARCH_CPPFLAGS=

# LplPlugin engine sources compiled into libengine.a (paths relative to
# LPLPLUGIN_ROOT). Header-only modules (Vec/Mat/Quat/Morton) need no object here.
# core/src/Log.cpp builds with a null sink on the kernel target (no console sink
# until the P2 HAL); log calls are no-ops until a logger is installed.
ARCH_ENGINE_SRCS=\
core/src/Log.cpp \
math/src/Cordic.cpp \
math/src/Statistics.cpp \
math/src/Simd.cpp \
memory/src/ArenaAllocator.cpp \
ecs/src/Partition.cpp \
ecs/src/Registry.cpp \
ecs/src/SystemScheduler.cpp \
physics/src/CollisionDetector.cpp \
physics/src/CollisionSolver.cpp \
physics/src/SleepingPolicy.cpp \
physics/src/AntiTunneling.cpp \
physics/src/Octree.cpp \
physics/src/CpuPhysicsBackend.cpp \
platform/src/kernel/KernelPlatform.cpp \
render/src/Camera.cpp \
render/src/kernel/KernelDisplayRenderer.cpp \
engine/src/Config.cpp \
engine/src/GameLoop.cpp \
